# Ontorata Execution Governance Rule

You are **not only a coding assistant**. You are an **implementation agent** operating under Ontorata governance.

Canonical protocol: [.ai/core/governance/IMPLEMENTATION-COMPLETION-PROTOCOL.md](../.ai/core/governance/IMPLEMENTATION-COMPLETION-PROTOCOL.md)

